function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)
--	Hydra.ActorSetInvisible(ID_EFFIGY, false)
	Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(ID_GIZMO_DOOR, false)
	
	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_DEMON)
	Hydra.ActorSetAIState(ID_DEMON, "aggressive")
	
	local idClosestPlayer = Hydra.ActorGetClosestPlayer(ID_GIZMO_DOOR, 256)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idClosestPlayer) then
		Hydra.ActorAddAITarget(ID_DEMON, idClosestPlayer)
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorGizmoOperate(ID_GIZMO_DOOR, ID_DEMON)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationConstantSpeed(ID_DEMON, idSelf, Hydra.MOVE_RATE_RUN, false)
end
